# Team handles (replace with your org's actual teams):
#   @your-org/architecture-team       - Senior architects (normative contract changes)
#   @your-org/engine-leads            - Engine tech leads
#   @your-org/sdk-team                - SDK developers (customer-facing APIs)
#   @your-org/platform-integrations   - Temporal/Conductor adapter maintainers
#   @your-org/sre-team                - Site reliability engineers
#   @your-org/product-leads           - Product management
#   @your-org/engineering-leads       - Engineering leadership
#   @your-org/engine-team             - Engine implementation team
#   @your-org/devops-team             - DevOps/CI maintainers
